Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向是無懈可擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從不會犯錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你把伯爵他們帶來巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵到底給你吃了什麼藥 說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 別太得意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個就輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家也會有災難降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為我是誰
