Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後會有期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事…
