Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 托您的福股票連日漲停
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息是自己飛來的 我本來也沒報什麼期望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 為數字的波動而忽悲忽喜真是浪費人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾福首席檢察官在眾目睽睽之下被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人吃驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世事無常不可預料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 聽說男爵和檢察官大人的甚有交情？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 根本談不上交情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男爵、莫爾塞夫將軍和維爾福檢察官是老相識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互利用來擴大權利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是這樣聽說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那只是別有用心之人的謠傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…人總有陰溝裏翻船的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男爵也最好注意一下人際關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對令嬡是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能早日收到佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是博尚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是記者先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 你運氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的獨家報導將會上頭版頭條
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何貴幹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們報社給重大獨家新聞的價碼是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於莫爾塞夫將軍的大醜聞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會吃驚的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這次要做莫爾塞夫候選人的特輯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盤算著靠私人交情打探點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問你些事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡力而為
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為父親是如何取得這般成就的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作為他身邊最親密的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能談談意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正直吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同深愛著母親一般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親深愛著國家 為國而憂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親誓死保衛了約阿尼納城 成為了英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到巴黎後 父親因此升階
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀輕輕就升至將軍之位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後終於能參選大統領
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親對政治的熱衷是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也祝你父親成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這時期 敵人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後請多留神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣靠小道消息吃飯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常會聽到奇怪的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賄賂啊 黑錢啊 情婦什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是煩透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親和那些事無緣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是成為政治家後可能有點固執過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點令人擔心罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真有那種事 我反而還會感動一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如：沒想到還有點本事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了些廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實今天有個奇怪的人找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個討厭的糟老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是卡德魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人和你說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼你父親在約阿尼納的表現有假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道 我把他趕走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏嚴禁煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻熄滅火種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是禁煙場所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請到指定的地點吸煙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去調查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙絕不會忘記我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約阿尼納事件有假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家也會有災難降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有請卡瓦爾坎蒂侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前您發表了向唐格拉爾銀行的巨額投資
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼使您做此決定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於投資 我是全權委託給顧問分析師的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全是遵從其意見行事 如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說您和唐格拉爾男爵的千金在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是私人問題 希望您能說說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就透露一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我和歐仁妮·德·唐格拉爾小姐今晨已正式訂婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 那真是恭喜您了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 這可是大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 要是知道你在我會彈的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然她也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐仁妮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 我有話要和歐仁妮說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我見她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐說不想和您說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想直接問她的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 至少告訴她我來過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐仁妮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有人來過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是送貨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不經過我同意就定下婚約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過 我最關心的是你的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你自己作主還太早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是說真的嗎 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:13:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐我邀請了卡瓦爾坎蒂侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用打那麼重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和歐仁妮已經完全結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和卡瓦爾坎蒂侯爵訂了婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是歐仁妮的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐仁妮不會願意和那樣的人訂婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是真 什麼是假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經搞不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼 我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 弗朗茲 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生了什麼 我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「人固有一死 惟各待其時」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吉之言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使為此而失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算暫時離開巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要去Luna了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這時候去旅行是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不能和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此有了秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也就此結束吧 弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密基地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會找出真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您身體沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完好如初
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連傘都不撐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想偶爾淋下雨也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我要去宇宙一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 您樂意同行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…今天還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您無需道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這副表情 我不能放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了您很久 晚餐已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您心中還是只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生去了新宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是打算和伯爵一起去避暑地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 祝賀的花來得讓人應接不暇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我送您的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼盡出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是真 什麼是假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是由您所決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有超越限界 勇往直前的覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有比任何人都強烈的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一定沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大統領選舉的有力競爭者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費爾南·德·莫爾塞夫將軍的公開演說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將在國民議會場舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許多名人前往支持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場內人氣高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫爾塞夫將軍 時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請上講台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有你相伴 我才能走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以您為榮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備車！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去議會場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開人們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和伯爵兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻無法逃避真實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 巖窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五幕\N幸福的終結、真實的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然後期待

